<ul class="download">
<li><a href="/KB/game/659044/ruleofready-Sep-28-2013.zip">Download source - 39 KB</a> </li>

<li><a href="https://ruleofready.codeplex.com/SourceControl/latest">Download latest version of source code (external link)</a> </li>
